target.description: On which target the jump occurs, the current Mini Program is defaulted
target.description_zh: 在哪个目标上发生跳转，默认当前小程序

url.description: The redirect link in the current Mini Program
url.description_zh: 当前小程序内的跳转链接

delta.description: Valid when open-type is 'navigateBack', indicating the number of layers to fall back
delta.description_zh: 当 open-type 为 'navigateBack' 时有效，表示回退的层数

appId.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the appId of the applet to be opened
appId.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，要打开的小程序 appId

path.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the page path is opened, and if it is empty, the home page is opened
path.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，打开的页面路径，如果为空则打开首页

extraData.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the data that needs to be passed to the target applet, and the target applet can get this data in App.onLaunch(),App.onShow().
extraData.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，需要传递给目标小程序的数据，目标小程序可在 App.onLaunch()，App.onShow() 中获取到这份数据.

version.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the version of the applet to be opened
version.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，要打开的小程序版本

hoverClass.description: Specifies the style class to press. When hover-class="none", there is no click-through effect
hoverClass.description_zh: 指定按下去的样式类。当 hover-class="none" 时，没有点击态效果

hoverStopPropagation.description: Specifies whether to prevent the native node of the node from being clicked
hoverStopPropagation.description_zh: 指定是否阻止本节点的祖先节点出现点击态

hoverStartTime.description: How long after you press and hold it to appear clicked, in milliseconds
hoverStartTime.description_zh: 按住后多久出现点击态，单位毫秒

hoverStayTime.description: The retention time of the click state after the finger is released, in milliseconds
hoverStayTime.description_zh: 手指松开后点击态保留时间，单位毫秒

shortLink.description: target="miniProgram" is valid, and app-id and path can be omitted when this parameter is passed. The link can be obtained through [Mini Program Menu] -> [Copy Link].
shortLink.description_zh: 当target="miniProgram"时有效，当传递该参数后，可以不传 app-id 和 path。链接可以通过【小程序菜单】->【复制链接】获取。

ariaLabel.description_zh: 无障碍访问，（属性）元素的额外描述

onSuccess.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the redirected to the mini program is successful
onSuccess.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，跳转小程序成功

onFail.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the jump to the mini program fails
onFail.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，跳转小程序失败

onComplete.description: When target="miniProgram" is valid, the jump to the mini program is completed
onComplete.description_zh: 当 target="miniProgram" 时有效，跳转小程序完成
